1.  Install and configure xdebug with php
2.  in /etc/php/7.4/apache2/php.ini add followimg lines below OPCache
 zend_extension = "<Location of xdebug.so file>"
xdebug.mode = debug
xdebug.start_with_request = yes
xdebug.client_port = 9000
xdebug.client_host = "127.0.0.1"
xdebug.log = "C:\xampp\tmp\xdebug\xdebug.log"
xdebug.idekey = VSCODE

after that install browser extension from below link 

https://xdebug.org/docs/step_debug

Refercences:

https://stackoverflow.com/questions/65137732/xdebug-v3-doesnt-stop-breakpoints-in-vscode
